268
00:17:49,827 --> 00:17:51,091
When?

269
00:17:51,688 --> 00:17:53,463
When the time is right.

270
00:18:21,186 --> 00:18:24,763
<i>I didn't know where I was or who had taken me.</i>

271
00:18:24,846 --> 00:18:28,623
<i>But it seemed the danger I had been warned of had finally come to pass.</i>

272
00:18:31,428 --> 00:18:34,432
<i>The memories that haunted me came flooding in again.</i>

273
00:18:36,026 --> 00:18:38,220
<i>Was I remembering my past...</i>

274
00:18:40,888 --> 00:18:43,381
