277
00:19:02,538 --> 00:19:04,472
Are you a religious family?

278
00:19:04,698 --> 00:19:06,593
I take it you're not.

279
00:19:06,677 --> 00:19:07,471
No.

280
00:19:07,716 --> 00:19:11,390
