but it got away from me over the years.

281
00:19:11,515 --> 00:19:13,220
Yeah, we never used to be either, but...

282
00:19:13,778 --> 00:19:18,431
When you lose a child, somehow you need a kind of higher power for comfort.

283
00:19:19,046 --> 00:19:21,170
I can't blame him for being scared.

284
00:19:21,317 --> 00:19:24,771
We're strangers to him,
and he's like a stranger to us.

285
00:19:27,277 --> 00:19:29,781
Maybe he's not the only one who's scared.

286
00:19:29,875 --> 00:19:32,772
What if those five years have changed him somehow?

287
00:19:33,305 --> 00:19:34,911
They've changed me.

288
00:19:35,757 --> 00:19:39,242
