433
00:29:59,397 --> 00:30:02,170
Just let him deal with it in his own way.

434
00:30:11,295 --> 00:30:12,642
Steven...

435
00:30:13,126 --> 00:30:14,732
What, Nicole?

436
00:30:15,356 --> 00:30:17,840
Can't I be just a little bit upset?

437
00:30:18,275 --> 00:30:21,021
