439
00:30:30,405 --> 00:30:33,771
Through this whole thing,
you haven't faltered.

440
00:30:34,498 --> 00:30:35,942
Not once.

441
00:30:36,108 --> 00:30:39,061
In my line of work, this is what you hope for.

442
00:30:39,408 --> 00:30:42,630
Most foster care stories don't have happy endings.

443
00:30:42,965 --> 00:30:47,451
For Kyle to be placed with his real parents and his memories coming back,

444
00:30:47,966 --> 00:30:49,672
