445
00:30:52,275 --> 00:30:57,320
Well, that's why you're my higher power.

446
00:31:05,875 --> 00:31:07,093
You okay?

447
00:31:07,748 --> 00:31:09,800
I'm totally not crying.

448
00:31:11,278 --> 00:31:13,470
Water proof mascara rules.

449
00:31:14,166 --> 00:31:15,561
