458
00:31:48,527 --> 00:31:49,502
Exactly.

459
00:31:52,618 --> 00:31:54,883
Have you seen Charlie? He just disappeared.

460
00:31:55,978 --> 00:31:59,483
He's inside...cleaning up.

461
00:32:02,556 --> 00:32:04,323
I can't believe you're leaving.

462
00:32:05,976 --> 00:32:07,733
I'll see you again, though.

463
00:32:08,085 --> 00:32:10,362
It's not like forever, right?

464
00:32:10,537 --> 00:32:12,393
I don't want it to be.

465
00:32:14,567 --> 00:32:15,692
Okay.

466
00:32:16,668 --> 00:32:18,613
Then no good-byes.

467
00:32:20,447 --> 00:32:22,131
No good-byes.

468
00:32:22,916 --> 00:32:26,952
Just, like...see ya.

469
00:32:28,865 --> 00:32:30,051
See ya.

470
00:32:49,158 --> 00:32:50,153
Come on.

471
00:33:04,097 --> 00:33:05,383
